==========>JENKINS PORT NUMBER CHANGE COMMANDS STEP BY STEP <==========

     1. cd /usr/lib/systemd/system

     2. ls

     3. vi jenkins.service =====>esc :set number====>enter=====>go to 70th nbr change jenkins PORT nbr =====>esc :wq! 
 
     4. systemctl restart jenkins

     5. systemctl status jenkins
     
     6. sudo systemctl daemon-reload 

     7. systemctl status jenkins

     8. sudo systemctl stop jenkins

     9. sudo systemctl start jenkins

    10. sudo systemctl status jenkins


TRIVY INSTALL Commands 

wget https://github.com/aquasecurity/trivy/releases/download/v0.38.3/trivy_0.38.3_Linux-64bit.deb

sudo dpkg -i trivy_0.38.3_Linux-64bit.deb

trivy --version



